ime":"2020-01-10T15:18:51.000Z","msg":"想知有無先例？"},{"pid":"89e6471188b74f0b8a45f4d2873f1dbaa5c30dd8","tid":1818942,"uid":61287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T15:23:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd979777df0d4677ebea81d3f93087c33787361a","tid":1818942,"uid":266755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T15:26:28.000Z","msg":"再幫推"},{"pid":"aaa6479c0142460366f333a342a345d7cf40fe4a","tid":1818942,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f73c35e4b2c22853ee9e9c2bff1c2af0e01482a9","tid":1818942,"uid":76365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T15:18:51.000Z","msg":"想知有無先例？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T15:56:08.000Z","msg":"South Africa's foreign trade and investment were affected by sanctions and boycotts, especially during the 1980s and early 1990s. These measures included a voluntary arms embargo instituted by the United Nations (UN) in 1963, which was declared mandatory in 1977; the 1978 prohibition of loans from the United States Export-Import Bank; an oil embargo first instituted by OPEC in 1973 and strengthened in a similar move by Iran in 1979; a 1983 prohibition on IMF loans; a 1985 cutoff of most foreign loans by private banks; the United States 1986 Comprehensive Antiapartheid Act, which limited trade and discouraged United States investors; and the 1986 European Economic Community (EEC) ban on trade and investment. The Organization of African Unity (OAU) also discouraged trade with South Africa, although observers estimated that Africa's officially unreported trade with South Africa exceeded R10 billion per year in the late 1980s.<br />\n<br />\n有南非<br />\n但唔係呢條法例"},{"pid":"1e1c35f20397813fb38c5afa06f0ed7728bdc109","tid":1818942,"uid":266755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T16:17:47.000Z","msg":"幫推之餘，亦有小小噏吓，因為［不要買香港股票］呢樣嘢喺好難實現。<br />\n<br />\n而亦想expand吓燒生idea(講得唔好或唔到就輕輕屌兩嘢算)，喺要target機構投資者，即各類基金，各大大小小基金都會每半年/三個月/一個月會對其投資組合調整(包括股、債券、期貨)，而how to pick the mix 就會考慮回報、年期等等，而有一撮基金assessment時會考慮埋其金融産品背後的實際源頭喺咪有侵犯人權，而呢啲正正就喺要做嘢的範疇。<br />\n<br />\n但呢啲要金融界內專業人仕先會熟啲。<br />\n當然，要整合嘅就喺例如<br />\n投資whitelist之類嘅嘢。"},{"pid":"48dd0279ccc598b2e2da842896ca9326d6015c39","tid":1818942,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T17:03:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38dc20f3ea72809492c758acd905ab96f88ae18","tid":1818942,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T17:08:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好難明但好有用咁 ， 幫推"},{"pid":"cbf1b08d823dda619aca6e95557152a688f056e9","tid":1818942,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T17:09:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d1d645c76bbcce1e3dddd4b49d5900b21c0ff87","tid":1818942,"uid":344793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T17:14:20.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n咁我地實際上要做啲乜? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d5e4190d61ca8df7a48c46270fbde5b98b0030","tid":1818942,"uid":228701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5af035df5e309495a923d00df81591bb99a6498","tid":1818942,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d0da1bb56c784bf68164b30622a41cb261a0175","tid":1818942,"uid":228701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T11:56:35.000Z","msg":"支持。<br />\n可以點推動呢件事？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T11:57:09.000Z","msg":"大家組織人去做, 無人去做, 手足既血與汗就白費了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T00:01:57.000Z","msg":"組織人去做，具體係要做乜嘢？"},{"pid":"d398d3d8db16784ffe0d8a825d620912600a870f","tid":1818942,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T03:33:35.000Z","m